snippet.title: Gunfire Reborn's First DLC "Visitors of Spirit Realm" Official Trailer
snippet.description: Gunfire Reborn's first paid DLC "Visitors of Spirit Realm" will be available on August 29. This DLC contains 2 new heroes - Xing Zhe (a monkey who is capable of casting celestial spells) and Li (a fox who can set her enemies ablaze with powerful flames). Also, 4 new weapons are included in the new content.
